-- Mattel says Barbie sales fell 12 pct
-- 
-- Thu Jan 31, 2008 9:08am EST
-- http://www.reuters.com/article/2008/01/31/us-mattel-barbie-idUSWEN368920080131

 

 NEW YORK  (Reuters) - Mattel Inc MAT.N said on Thursday that U.S. Barbie sales fell 12 percent during the fourth quarter. 

 Chief Executive Robert Eckert called Barbie's performance for the full year a "disappointment" on a conference call. (Reporting by  Justin Grant , editing by Gerald E. McCormick)